articles.title: Doctors seeing strokes more often in young people - NBC4 WCMH-TV
articles.description: COLUMBUS, Ohio (WCMH) – Doctors are seeing a serious and often deadly type of stroke more often in young and middle-aged adults, according to the American Heart Association. It said the rate among this age group is growing faster than in older people. Medical…
